author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-WSE Excludes Shares Of Alma Market From Trading As Of June 3
text:
May 30 (Reuters) - ALMA MARKET SA W RESTRUKTURYZACJI
* WARSAW STOCK EXCHANGE (WSE) DECIDED ON TUESDAY TO EXCLUDE SHARES OF ALMA MARKET SA FROM TRADING ON MAIN MARKET AS OF JUNE 3
* WSE SET JUNE 1 AS THE LAST DAY OF TRADING OF ALMA MARKET SHARES
